      "because when `x_i = 1`, `x_j = -1`, `‚ąö|x_i + x_j| + ‚ąö|x_j + x_i| = 0 + 0`, while `‚ąö|x_i - x_j| + ‚ąö|x_j - x_i| = 2‚ąö",
      "\n  have h‚āĀ : ‚ąÄ (i j : Fin n), ‚ąö|x i - x j| ‚Č§ ‚ąö|x i + x j| := by\n    intro i j\n    have h‚āā : |x i - x j| ‚Č§ |x i + x j| := by\n      cases' le_total 0 (x i - x j) with h‚āÉ h‚āÉ <;>\n        cases' le_total 0 (x i + x j) with h‚āĄ h‚āĄ <;>\n          cases' le_total (x i - x j) 0 with h‚āÖ h‚āÖ <;>\n            cases' le_total (x i + x j) 0 with h‚āÜ h‚āÜ <;>\n              simp_all only [abs_of_nonneg, abs_of_nonpos, sub_nonneg, sub_nonpos] <;>\n                (try { contradiction }) <;>\n                  (try { nlinarith }) <;>\n                    (try {\n                      cases' le_total (x i + x j) 0 with h‚āá h‚āá <;>\n                        cases' le_total (x i - x j) 0 with h‚āą h‚āą <;>\n                          simp_all [abs_of_nonneg, abs_of_nonpos, sub_nonneg, sub_nonpos] <;>\n                            nlinarith\n                    }) <;>\n                    (try {\n                      cases' le_total (x i + x j) 0 with h‚āá h‚āá <;>\n                        cases' le_total (x i - x j) 0 with h‚āą h‚āą <;>\n                          simp_all [abs_of_nonneg, abs_of_nonpos, sub_nonneg, sub_nonpos] <;>\n                            nlinarith\n                    })\n    apply Real.sqrt_le_sqrt\n    exact h‚āā\n  calc\n    ‚ąĎ i : Fin n, ‚ąĎ j : Fin n, ‚ąö|x i - x j| ‚Č§ ‚ąĎ i : Fin n, ‚ąĎ j : Fin n, ‚ąö|x i + x j| := by\n      exact Finset.sum_le_sum fun i _ => Finset.sum_le_sum fun j _ => h‚āĀ i j\n    _ = ‚ąĎ i, ‚ąĎ j, ‚ąö|x i + x j| := by rfl",
      "\n  have h‚āĀ : ‚ąÄ i j : Fin n, ‚ąö|x i - x j| ‚Č§ ‚ąö|x i + x j| := by\n    intro i j\n    have h‚āā : |x i - x j| ‚Č§ |x i + x j| := by\n      cases' le_total 0 (x i - x j) with h‚āÉ h‚āÉ <;>\n        cases' le_total 0 (x i + x j) with h‚āĄ h‚āĄ <;>\n          cases' le_total 0 (x i) with h‚āÖ h‚āÖ <;>\n            cases' le_total 0 (x j) with h‚āÜ h‚āÜ <;>\n              simp_all only [abs_of_nonneg, abs_of_nonpos, sub_nonneg, sub_nonpos] <;>\n                (try { contradiction }) <;>\n                  (try { linarith }) <;>\n                    (try\n                      {\n                        cases' le_total 0 (x i + x j) with h‚āá h‚āá <;>\n                          cases' le_total 0 (x i - x j) with h‚āą h‚āą <;>\n                            simp_all [abs_of_nonneg, abs_of_nonpos, sub_nonneg, sub_nonpos] <;>\n                              linarith\n                      })\n    -- Use the fact that the square root function is monotonically increasing\n    apply Real.sqrt_le_sqrt\n    exact h‚āā\n  -- Summing over all pairs (i, j)\n  calc\n    ‚ąĎ i : Fin n, ‚ąĎ j : Fin n, ‚ąö|x i - x j| ‚Č§ ‚ąĎ i : Fin n, ‚ąĎ j : Fin n, ‚ąö|x i + x j| := by\n      exact Finset.sum_le_sum fun i _ => Finset.sum_le_sum fun j _ => h‚āĀ i j\n    _ = ‚ąĎ i : Fin n, ‚ąĎ j : Fin n, ‚ąö|x i + x j| := by rfl",
